==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Self-abuse
<hw>Self`-abuse"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
abuse of one's own self, powers, or faculties.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Self-deception; delusion.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Masturbation; onanism; self-pollution.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Self-accused</ent>⟦br⟧
